  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a punishment-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] auxiliary, labor auxiliary, in what used to be the hotel, the back yard of which abutted the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were supposed to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a-- there was a little [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] kind of walkway created by two sets of-- of planks or-- or-- or wood, which we were supposed to-- within which we were supposed to patrol.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one side was open into that-- the backyard of this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] former hotel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we communicated-- we had somehow managed to communicate with-- with these more mature people who were in the-- in the camp, and again, attempting to try to devise some fashion or some way of-- of escape and-- and of organizing or resisting.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was all a very macabre kind of thing because there really was not much reality to it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There couldn't have been.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We did also prepare a couple of-- a couple of hiding places for people who were willing to-- to hide without-- when-- when we sort of realized and knew that we were going to be deported.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in fact, just in preparation for this recording, at your request, I was looking at some pictures [INAUDIBLE] against of one of the-- at the pictures of the person who was the [INAUDIBLE] of [INAUDIBLE] in-- in Kisvarda who hid out in one of the places that we prepared and-- and survived and came to-- to Palestine in-- in I think already in '45.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
